OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Frather cloudy evening with showers,
OL,7,Fsome of these heavy at first. Further
OL,8,Fshowery outbreaks of rain will spread
OL,9,Fin from the west through the early
OL,10,Fhours.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA rather cloudy day with
OL,13,Fscattered showers, occasionally heavy
OL,14,Fat times. Some sunnier spells,
OL,15,Fespecially early and late in the day.
OL,16,FBreezy, especially around coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
