OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FMainly
OL,6,Fdry and bright during this period. A
OL,7,Ffew sunnier spells at times but cloud
OL,8,Ftending to bubble up during daytime.
OL,9,FLighter winds than of late but
OL,10,Fbreezier by Tuesday.
